\c 6
\s Ukuchithwa kweJeriko
\p
\v 1 IJeriko yayivaliwe-ke ngci ngenxa yabantwana bakoIsrayeli. Kakho owaphumayo, njalo kakho owangenayo.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuJoshuwa: Bona, nginikele esandleni sakho iJeriko lenkosi yayo lamaqhawe\x + Dute. 7.24. 2.24.\x* alamandla\x + 1.14.\x*.
\v 3 Lizawubhoda-ke umuzi, wonke amadoda empi, awubhode umuzi kanye. Uzakwenza njalo insuku eziyisithupha.
\v 4 Labapristi abayisikhombisa bazathwala impondo\x + Hlu. 7.16,22.\x* zenqama eziyisikhombisa\x + 6.6,8,13; 6.5.\x* phambi komtshokotsho; kuthi ngosuku lwesikhombisa lizawubhoda umuzi kasikhombisa, labapristi bevuthela impondo\x + Nani 10.8.\x*.
\v 5 Kuzakuthi-ke lapho bekhalisa uphondo lwenqama isikhathi eside\x + Eks. 19.13. Hlu. 20.37.\x*, nxa lisizwa ukukhala kophondo, abantu bonke bazamemeza ngokuklabalala okukhulu, lomduli womuzi uzadilikela phansi; labantu bazakwenyuka, ngulowo lalowo maqondana laye.
\p
\v 6 Ngakho uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni wabiza abapristi wathi kibo: Thwalani umtshokotsho wesivumelwano, labapristi abayisikhombisa bathwale impondo zezinqama eziyisikhombisa phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 7 Wasesithi ebantwini: Dlulani liwuzingelezele umuzi, lohlomileyo kadlule phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 8 Kwasekusithi uJoshuwa esekhulume ebantwini, abapristi abayisikhombisa bethwele impondo eziyisikhombisa zenqama bakhokhela phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, bavuthela impondo, lomtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* wabalandela.
\v 9 Abahlomileyo basebehamba phambi kwabapristi ababevuthela izimpondo, lesigaba sasemuva salandela umtshokotsho, bahamba bevuthela izimpondo.
\v 10 UJoshuwa wayelaye-ke abantu esithi: Lingamemezi, loba lizwakalise ilizwi lenu; kungaphumi lizwi emlonyeni wenu kuze kube lusuku engizalitshela ngalo ukuthi limemeze; beselimemeza.
\v 11 Ngakho umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* wawubhoda umuzi, uzingelezela kanye; basebesiza enkambeni, balala enkambeni ebusuku.
\p
\v 12 UJoshuwa wasevuka ekuseni kakhulu, labapristi bathwala umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Nani 4.15.\x*.
\v 13 Labapristi abayisikhombisa bephethe impondo zezinqama eziyisikhombisa phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* baqhubeka behamba, bevuthela izimpondo, labahlomileyo bahamba phambi kwabo, lesigaba sasemuva salandela umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*, bahamba bevuthela izimpondo.
\v 14 Langosuku lwesibili bawuzingelezela umuzi kanye, babuyela enkambeni. Benza njalo insuku eziyisithupha.
\v 15 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesikhombisa bavuka ngovivi emadabukakusa, bawubhoda umuzi kasikhombisa ngendlela efananayo. Kuphela ngalolosuku bawubhoda umuzi kasikhombisa.
\v 16 Kwasekusithi ngesikhathi sesikhombisa, abapristi bavuthela impondo, uJoshuwa wasesithi ebantwini: Memezani, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilinikile umuzi.
\v 17 Kodwa umuzi wona lakho konke okukuwo kuzakwehlukaniselwa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; nguRahabi iwule kuphela ozaphila, yena labo bonke alabo endlini yakhe, ngoba wafihla izithunywa esazithumayo\x + 2.4.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa lina sibili zigcineni kokuqalekisiweyo, hlezi lizenze abaqalekisiweyo nxa lithatha kokuqalekisiweyo, lenze inkamba yakoIsrayeli ibe yinto eqalekisiweyo\x + 2.4.\x*, liyihluphe\x + Gen. 34.30. Josh. 7.25. 1 Kho. 18.17,18. 1 Lan. 2.7.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa sonke isiliva legolide, lezitsha zethusi lezensimbi, kungcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Kuzakuza endlini yokuligugu kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 20 Abantu basebememeza, kwavuthelwa izimpondo. Kwasekusithi abantu besizwa ukukhala kwempondo, abantu bamemeza ngokuklabalala okukhulu, umduli wadilikela phansi, labantu benyukela emzini, ngulowo lalowo maqondana laye, bawuthumba umuzi\x + 6.5. Heb. 11.30.\x*.
\v 21 Batshabalalisa konke okusemzini, kusukela kowesilisa kusiya kowesifazana, kusukela komutsha kusiya komdala, kuze kube senkabini lemvini lobabhemi, ngobukhali benkemba\x + Dute. 7.2.\x*.
\v 22 Lakulawomadoda amabili ayeyehlola ilizwe uJoshuwa wathi: Ngenani endlini yowesifazana oliwule, likhuphe kuyo owesifazana lakho konke alakho, njengokufunga kwenu kuye\x + 2.14. Heb. 11.31.\x*.
\v 23 Lamajaha izinhloli angena akhupha uRahabi loyise lonina labanewabo lakho konke ayelakho; akhupha zonke izihlobo zakhe, azibeka ngaphandle kwenkamba yakoIsrayeli\x + 2.13.\x*.
\v 24 Basebewutshisa umuzi ngomlilo lakho konke okwakukiwo; kuphela isiliva legolide lezitsha zethusi lezensimbi bakufaka kokuligugu kwendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 6.19.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho uRahabi iwule, lendlu kayise, labo bonke ayelabo, uJoshuwa wabayekela bephila; wahlala phakathi koIsrayeli kuze kube lamuhla, ngoba wafihla izithunywa uJoshuwa ayezithume ukuhlola iJeriko\x + Mat. 1.5.\x*.
\p
\v 26 UJoshuwa wa\add ba\add*fungisa esithi\x + Nani 5.21.\x*: Uqalekisiwe umuntu phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* osukuma akhe lumuzi iJeriko. Uzawusekela ngezibulo lakhe, amise amasango awo ngecinathunjana lakhe\x + 1 Kho. 16.34.\x*.
\v 27 Ngokunjalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yaba loJoshuwa\x + 1.5.\x*, lodumo lwakhe lwaba selizweni lonke\x + 9.9.\x*.